issue.title: Set up route for swiping left or right
issue.body:
Add to swipedLeft or swipedRight.  If right, and in candidate's swipedRight, add to both people's matches list, indicate a match in the return object.

POST /users/swipe
- id of candidate
- "left" or "right"

return

{ match: bool }

issue.title: Set up route for getting new match
issue.body:
Given logged in user, shuffle all users, filter for those not in swipedLeft or swipedRight.

GET /users/newCandidate
